value:
These clothes are in an ancient style
that matches the ones worn by the
progenitor—I mean by Sothis.

The goddess Sothis once dwelt
within me.

I'm often told I don't show much
emotion, but I've never thought of
myself as an "Ashen Demon."

The Officers Academy made me who
I am today. It's all thanks to my
wonderful students.
I'll use this power for the greater good.

I hope I'm not intruding. I was
asked to come say hello by
your friend $Nf.
With the goddess!
Just like that. Stay focused.
I'm not setting a very good example...

There is an endless amount of
knowledge out there. I hope to
never stop learning.

In time’s flow, see the glow of flames
ever burning bright... On the swift
river’s drift, broken memories alight...$k$pWhen we bring our voices together,
we can conquer the very heavens.

Time's flow... A place where all the
possibilities of fate seem to lie,
stretching out into infinity.$k$pTwisting through time, a glimpse of
destiny... What did I see there? What
did I know? What did I accomplish?$k$pWearing these clothes puts me in the
mood to think about these mysteries.
The mystery of power most of all.$k$pI don't want to dwell too much on the
past. That much is clear. I need to
keep moving forward.$k$pWe cannot accept the status quo.
War cannot be the norm. Not in
Fódlan, nor in Askr.$k$pI know the Heroes of this world feel
the same way. And their brave voices
inspire me to fight for change.
With the goddess!
You go no further!
Have faith!
Stay where you are!
Forgive me, everyone...
This garb matches that of Sothis.
Hm? Your hand is cold. Are you well?
I heard countless voices calling me here...though their origin remains a mystery to me.
It's not that I feel embarrassed, but... Is it appropriate to hold class in this attire?
The goddess Sothis once dwelled within me. I understand if that is hard to believe.
Could this be where the flow of time has guided me next on my journey?
Let us continue working together to build a better world.
Good idea.
Hmm...
I go with conviction.
